<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Features - MIGS List | Union Member Management</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body class="features-page">
  <div class="features-container">
    <nav class="features-nav">
      <a href="/" class="nav-brand-link">
        <img src="/logo.png" alt="MigsList" class="nav-logo">
        <span>MIGS List</span>
      </a>
      <div class="nav-actions">
        <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-primary">Start Free Trial</a>
        <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline">Sign In</a>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <header class="features-header">
      <h1>Powerful Features for Union Locals</h1>
      <p>Everything you need to manage your members and track good standing status.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"></path>
            <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"></circle>
            <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"></path>
            <path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Member Management</h3>
        <p>Keep all your union members organized with detailed contact information, addresses, and status tracking. Never lose track of a member again.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M22 19a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h5l2 3h9a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Bucket Organization</h3>
        <p>Organize members into buckets based on your union's structure - by department, location, job classification, or any grouping you need.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"></path>
            <polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"></polyline>
            <line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"></line>
            <line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"></line>
            <polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>PDF Document Tracking</h3>
        <p>Upload signed documents for each member. Instantly see who's in good standing and who still needs to submit their paperwork.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
            <line x1="3" y1="9" x2="21" y2="9"></line>
            <line x1="9" y1="21" x2="9" y2="9"></line>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Excel Export</h3>
        <p>Generate professional Excel reports of your members. Filter by good standing status and share with management or headquarters easily.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"></path>
            <polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Email Documents</h3>
        <p>Send master PDF documents directly to members who need to submit paperwork. One-click email with document attached.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Role-Based Access</h3>
        <p>Presidents have full control while Secretaries handle data entry. Keep your union's data secure with proper access controls.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"></line>
            <line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"></line>
            <line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"></line>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Compliance Tracking</h3>
        <p>See at-a-glance compliance rates for each bucket. Bright green percentages show you exactly where your union stands.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"></circle>
            <polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Always Available</h3>
        <p>Access your member data 24/7 from anywhere. Cloud-hosted and secure, your data is always at your fingertips.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="features-cta">
      <h2>Ready to streamline your union's member management?</h2>
      <p>Start your free 30-day trial today. No credit card required.</p>
      <a href="/signup" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Start Free Trial</a>
    </div>

    <footer class="features-footer">
      <p>&copy; 2024 MigsList. Built for union locals.</p>
    </footer>
  </div>

  <style>
    .features-page {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: var(--bg-secondary);
    }
    .features-container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 2rem;
    }
    .features-nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1.5rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    }
    .nav-brand-link {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .nav-logo {
      height: 40px;
      width: auto;
    }
    .nav-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .features-header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 4rem 0;
    }
    .features-header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .features-header p {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
    }
    .features-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }
    .feature-card {
      background: var(--bg-primary);
      padding: 2rem;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }
    .feature-icon {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      background: var(--primary);
      border-radius: 12px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .feature-icon svg {
      width: 24px;
      height: 24px;
      color: white;
    }
    .feature-card h3 {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }
    .feature-card p {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .features-cta {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 4rem 2rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--primary-dark) 100%);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      color: white;
      margin-bottom: 4rem;
    }
    .features-cta h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }
    .features-cta p {
      opacity: 0.9;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .btn-lg {
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      font-size: 1.125rem;
    }
    .features-footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem 0;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border-color);
      color: var(--text-secondary);
    }
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .features-header h1 {
        font-size: 1.75rem;
      }
      .nav-actions {
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 0.5rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</body>
</html>
